

<div class="p-6 sm:px-20 bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
    <div>
        <!-- This is the logo & title seen on the dashboard
         To update this you need to access the vendor/jetstream components
         running command: php artisan vendor:publish --tag=jetstream-views
         will give you access to jetstream components to edit.
         the logos will take SVG or imgs sourced in the project.
         Example: Vendor/jetstream/components/application.logo.blade
        -->
        <x-jet-application-logo class="block h-12 w-auto" />
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-2xl">
        Welcome to the open source Donation Tracker!
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 text-gray-500">
        This app is a tracking and reporting tool for your local place of worship. The app is able to record donations for recordkeeping & tax purposes.
    </div>
</div>

